                <li>People honerly call them “Babasaheb”.</li>
                <li>Such a great student, lawyer, politician and economist born n 14 April 1891.</li>
                <li>His father name is Ramji maloji sakpal as well as his mother name is bhimaji ramji sakpal.</li>
                <li>From childhood babasaheb was brilliant student.</li>
                <li>Babasaheb ambedkar completed his B.A. and M.A. from university of Mumbai.</li>
                <li>They had completed barrister at law, Msc. in economics, Phd. In economies.</li>
                <li>They had moved dalit into Buddisth in 1956.</li>
